    <h3>What is Predicts Hit?</h3>
      <div>
        Predicts Hit is a prediction market platform designed to make predicting the outcome of events with friends simple, quick, and fun. Predicts Hit provides the tools for you to compete with friends to predict the outcome of anything you want. Who among you is best at forecasting the outcomes during a sport season? Who has been keeping track of the best teams for your crew's favorite video game? Who is able to anticipate the future winner of your favorite reality tv show? Predicts Hit allows you to measure your ability to predict whatever it is you want to predict.
