    <h3>What is our mission?</h3>
      <div>
       Our goal is to enable small groups of people to effortlessly compete amongst each other to see who can most consistently and accurately predict outcomes. We want to give groups who enjoy debating what is going to happen during their favorite events to have a physical, concrete way of measuring their predictions. Essentially, we want to take friendly wagers to the next level.
